---
title: Creamy Tuscan Beef and Penne with Kale and Parmesan
description: Does the thought of a big bowl of pasta put a smile on your face? We’re right there with you. Quick, comforting, and the perfect carby canvas for a multitude of delicious toppings--it’s essentially a hug disguised as dinner. … This dish proves our point. Al dente penne is tossed in a rich, creamy meat sauce studded with hearty kale and sprinkled with nutty Parmesan and bright scallion greens. Our chefs guarantee it’ll make stomachs happy.
